### Product Category Best Practices

#### **Electronics/Tech**
- Emphasize innovation and performance
- Specs matter but translate to benefits
- Compare to older models or competition
- Highlight ease of use despite complexity
- Include compatibility information

#### **Fashion/Apparel**
- Focus on style, comfort, versatility
- Describe fit and materials sensory
- Suggest styling options
- Size guide clarity
- Care instructions briefly

#### **Home/Furniture**
- Emphasize lifestyle improvement
- Dimensions with context
- Material quality and durability
- Assembly requirements
- Design aesthetic fit

#### **Beauty/Personal Care**
- Ingredients/formulation benefits
- Results and timeline
- Skin/hair type suitability
- Scent descriptions (if applicable)
- Application instructions

#### **Food/Beverage**
- Taste descriptions (sensory)
- Sourcing and quality
- Nutritional highlights
- Serving suggestions
- Storage/preparation

#### **Toys/Games**
- Age appropriateness
- Educational value
- Fun factor
- Safety certifications
- Replay value

