- Bullet points are critical
- Focus on searchability
- Technical specs prominent
- Customer questions anticipated

**Shopify/E-commerce**:
- More storytelling room
- Lifestyle imagery suggestions
- Cross-sell opportunities
- Brand building

**Marketplaces**:
